OL,3,CHarry Styles says he struggles to
OL,4,Cspeak about former bandmate Liam
OL,5,CPayne's death
OL,7,FFormer One Direction star Harry Styles
OL,8,Fhas said he struggles to speak about
OL,9,Fthe death of bandmate Liam Payne.
OL,11,FIt comes as the 32-year-old, from
OL,12,FHolmes Chapel in Cheshire, prepares to
OL,13,Frelease his fourth studio album, Kiss
OL,14,FAll The Time, Disco, Occasionally, on
OL,15,FFriday.
OL,17,FStyles told Apple Music's Zane Lowe
OL,18,Fthat the album was inspired by moments
OL,19,Fwhen his favourite artists had to
OL,20,F"discover themselves" and where they
OL,21,Fwere "vulnerable".
OL,26,@|D@AOU|D@UO]}D@FOU}D@QO]
