OL,3,CHarry Styles says he struggles to
OL,4,Cspeak about former bandmate Liam
OL,5,CPayne's death
OL,7,FAsked about Payne's death, Styles
OL,8,Fsaid: "Full transparency, it's like
OL,9,Fsomething that I, even the idea of
OL,10,Ftalking about it, I struggle with that
OL,11,Fa little bit even.
OL,13,F"I think there was a period when he
OL,14,Fpassed away, where I really struggled
OL,15,Fwith kind of like acknowledging how
OL,16,Fstrange it is to have people kind of
OL,17,Flike own part of your grief in a way.
OL,26,@pD@GOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772705110
OL,3,CHarry Styles says he struggles to
OL,4,Cspeak about former bandmate Liam
OL,5,CPayne's death
OL,7,F"I have such strong feelings around my
OL,8,Ffriend passing away, and then suddenly
OL,9,Fbeing, you know, like aware of there's
OL,10,Fmaybe like a desire from other people
OL,11,Fof you to convey that in some way, or
OL,12,Fit means you're not feeling what
OL,13,Fyou're feeling or something, you know?
OL,15,F"It's so difficult to lose a friend.
OL,16,FIt's difficult to lose any friend, but
OL,17,Fit's so difficult to lose a friend who
OL,18,Fis so like you in so many ways. It's
OL,19,Flike, I saw someone with the kindest
OL,20,Fheart who just wanted to be great.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
