PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772705110
OL,3,CHarry Styles says he struggles to
OL,4,Cspeak about former bandmate Liam
OL,5,CPayne's death
OL,7,F"It was a really important moment for
OL,8,Fme in terms of taking a look at my
OL,9,Flife and being able to say to myself,
OL,10,F'OK, what do I want to do with my
OL,11,Flife? How do I want to live my life?'.
OL,13,F"And I think the greatest way you can
OL,14,Fhonour your friends who pass away is
OL,15,Fby living your life to the fullest.
OL,16,FLike super special person and really
OL,17,Fsad."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUyD@EO]
