CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772705110
OL,3,CHarry Styles says he struggles to
OL,4,Cspeak about former bandmate Liam
OL,5,CPayne's death
OL,7,FPayne died at the age of 31 in October
OL,8,F2024 after falling from a hotel
OL,9,Fbalcony in Argentina, and the
OL,10,Fboyband's surviving members, Styles,
OL,11,FNiall Horan, Louis Tomlinson and Zayn
OL,12,FMalik, reunited at his funeral
OL,13,Falongside former manager Simon Cowell
OL,14,Fin November that year.
OL,16,FStyles said that his time out between
OL,17,FKiss All The Time, Disco,
OL,18,FOccasionally, and previous record
OL,19,FHarry's House (2022) allowed him to
OL,20,Freflect on his career as he turned 30.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
