PN,39306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772705110
OL,3,CHarry Styles says he struggles to
OL,4,Cspeak about former bandmate Liam
OL,5,CPayne's death
OL,7,FThe singer added: "I've always had the
OL,8,Fconversation with myself about if I
OL,9,Fever checked in with myself and was
OL,10,Flike, 'I don't love it, it's not fun
OL,11,Fanymore', then I kind of just made a
OL,12,Fpromise to myself that I wouldn't do
OL,13,Fit.
OL,15,F"I don't think it's fair in a lot of
OL,16,Fways, I don't think it's fair to me, I
OL,17,Freally don't think it's fair to the
OL,18,Ffans for me to not do it, (not) really
OL,19,Fbe there anymore, but doing it because
OL,20,Fit's just what I've always done.
OL,26,@oD@SOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
