OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772705110
OL,3,CHarry Styles says he struggles to
OL,4,Cspeak about former bandmate Liam
OL,5,CPayne's death
OL,7,F"And I think what has been interesting
OL,8,Fis kind of allowing myself to even
OL,9,Fhave that thought process. I think for
OL,10,Fa long time even having that
OL,11,Fconversation with myself, I thought
OL,12,Flike, 'oh you're so ungrateful like
OL,13,Fhow can you ever think about deciding
OL,14,Fnot to do it', and stuff like that."
OL,16,FThe full interview can be heard on
OL,17,FApple Music's The Zane Lowe Show.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@dO]
